name: BMO US Put Write ETF
longDescription: BMO US Put Write ETF writes put options on the equity securities of U.S. companies in a variety of sectors. See Investment Objectives Investment Objectives of the Non Index BMO ETFs BMO US Put Write ETF. The fund invests primarily in a portfolio of put options on US large capitalization equity securities to generate income.
